highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Ahmedabad. “Jhoome Jo Pathaan” is the highest at #3.
“Kahani Suno 2.0” by Kaifi Khalil is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Ahmedabad, up 49 spots at #32.
“Tu Aake Dekhle” by King has been on Top Songs Ahmedabad the longest, at 68 weeks straight.
“Tu Mile Dil Khile” by Asees Kaur and Stebin Ben is the highest new entry on Top Songs Ahmedabad at #19.
